# AUD-IMPL-018: keep test files OUT of the prod Spark image. The Dockerfile
# `COPY silver/ gold/` sweeps whole directories, and the v4-silver/v4-gold
# CronWorkflows (infra/helm/cronworkflows/templates/spark-v4.yaml) glob
# /opt/brain/{silver,gold}/*.py — a baked-in *_test.py would be spark-submitted
# as a mart (and pytest is NOT installed in the image, so v4-gold would abort
# mid-run). The submit loops also skip *_test.py (defense-in-depth); this keeps
# the image itself clean. deploy.yml builds with context: db/iceberg/spark, so
# this file governs that build.
**/*_test.py
**/__pycache__/
